					<![CDATA[
						 <p><em>&quot;She hasn't even been born yet, much less classified by your Foundation&#8230;&quot;</em></p> <p>Thank you to the outstanding individuals who helped me return to the site after nearly 8 years without an article! This goes doubly so for <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/uraniumempire" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1613974&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1583786333" alt="UraniumEmpire" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1613974)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/uraniumempire" >UraniumEmpire</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/zoobeeny" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6070624&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1583786333" alt="Zoobeeny" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6070624)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/zoobeeny" >Zoobeeny</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/dr-moned" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5596963&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1583786333" alt="Dr Moned" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5596963)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/dr-moned" >Dr Moned</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/popsioak" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5231418&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1583786333" alt="Popsioak" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5231418)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/popsioak" >Popsioak</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/frygeist" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3717153&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1583786333" alt="Frygeist" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3717153)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/frygeist" >Frygeist</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/gerrymanderbassist" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2346106&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1583786333" alt="GerrymanderBassist" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2346106)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/gerrymanderbassist" >GerrymanderBassist</a></span>and many more!</p> <p>A few spoilers -</p> <div class="collapsible-block"> <div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">The&nbsp;Spoilers</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none"> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">Access&nbsp;Granted</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-content"> <p><br /> 1) The [REDACTED] threat is none other than SCP-One Billion, first mentioned in SCP-990.</p> <p>2) Hattic was chosen because that was the language spoken in one of the locations that's theorized to feature the oldest known blacksmithing site.</p> <p>3) The Weapon has both physical and <em>pata</em>physical components.</p> </div> </div> </div> <p>Thanks for reading!</p> 
				 	]]>
